This project is a re-implementation of much of the functionality from
Izumiko/Jellyfin-Danmaku (https://github.com/Izumiko/Jellyfin-Danmaku),
including (but not limited to) the dandanplay match flow, the CORS-proxy
fallback, the source-tag classification, the comment de-duplication
heuristic, and the anti-overlap lane filter. Significant portions of the
algorithmic design are derived from that project. We strongly encourage
users of this script to also acknowledge and support the upstream
project.

